                "     As the 840 keV gamma ray from the Mn-54 decay",
                "has about the same energy as the 810 keV gamma ray",
                "in Co-58 decay, a comparison was made between the",
                "induced radioactivities in iron and nickel.",
                "From the intensity ratio of the photopeaks of the Mn-54",
                "and Co-58 gamma rays of about 1 to 50, the ratio of",
                "integrated neutron flux, the difference in number of",
                "target nuclei and growth factor, the cross sections",
                "of (n,p) reactions in Fe-54 and Ni-58 were found to Be",
                "the same within 10 %."
              ]
            }
          ],
